# ClinicOS Project Memory

## Project Overview
ClinicOS (क्लिनिक ओएस) is a cloud-based SaaS platform for Indian specialty clinics.
- **Target:** Dermatology, Physiotherapy, Dental, Ophthalmology, Orthopaedics, ENT, Gynaecology
- **Company:** RH Technology, Pune, Maharashtra
- **MVP Focus:** Dermatology + Physiotherapy + Dental (highest volume specialties)

## Tech Stack
| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Backend API | PHP 8.x + Laravel 11 |
| Database | MySQL 8 + Redis + AWS S3 |
| Web Frontend | React.js + Next.js (planned) |
| Mobile App | Flutter 3.x (tablet + phone) |
| Payments | Razorpay |
| WhatsApp | Meta Cloud API (WhatsApp Business) |
| AI | OpenAI Whisper (STT) + Claude API (field mapping) |
| ABDM | NHA ABDM APIs (ABHA, HFR, FHIR R4) |

