## ABDM Integration Milestones
- **M1:** ABHA creation/linking, facility QR code
- **M2:** HIP - FHIR R4 health record sharing
- **M3:** HIU - Receive records from other providers

## Coding Standards

### Backend (Laravel)
- Use Eloquent relationships properly
- Always scope queries with clinic_id for multi-tenancy
- Add extensive logging for debugging
- Follow PSR-12 coding standard
- Use Form Requests for validation

### Mobile (Flutter)
- Use Riverpod for state management
- Use go_router for navigation
- Follow feature-first folder structure
- Use Dio + Retrofit for API calls
- Add comprehensive logging

### Logging Rule (User Preference)
**IMPORTANT:** Add console.log / Log::info() extensively throughout all files for debugging purposes.

