## Key Business Rules
- Invoice numbers: CLNXXX-YYYY-NNNN format
- ABHA format: 14-digit (91-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX)
- Tooth notation: FDI (11-48 permanent, 51-85 primary)
- Appointment status flow: booked → confirmed → checked_in → in_consultation → completed
